的错误一面”，其他人 <a href="https://x.com/JeremyDanielBo1/status/1895991528058912906" target="_blank" rel="noopener">则说，</a>竞争对手的摔跤公司应在下一项活动中进行<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kendrick-lamar">Kendrick Lamar</a> 。</p><p>在拉马尔（Lamar）在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kendrick-lamar-hit-out-at-drake-during-super-bowl-halftime-show-2025-performance-i-want-to-play-their-favourite-song-but-you-know-they-like-to-sue-3836386">超级碗半场表演</a>中演出后，两人之间的争执最近发烧，这使他成为了有史以来第一个成为头条新闻的独奏说唱歌手。他借此机会在德雷克（Drake）拍摄了几枪，这让球迷们感到高兴。 </p><figure id="attachment_3837602" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3837602" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3837602" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KendrickLamarnewsong-Captain-America-Brave-New-World.jpg" alt="肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）在超级碗舞台上现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KendrickLamarnewsong-Captain-America-Brave-New-World.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KendrickLamarnewsong-Captain-America-Brave-New-World-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KendrickLamarnewsong-Captain-America-Brave-New-World-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KendrickLamarnewsong-Captain-America-Brave-New-World-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KendrickLamarnewsong-Captain-America-Brave-New-World-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KendrickLamarnewsong-Captain-America-Brave-New-World-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3837602" class="wp-caption-text">肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）在超级碗比赛中现场表演。图片来源：迈克尔·欧文斯/盖蒂</figcaption></figure><p>他取笑了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-sues-for-defamation-over-kendrick-lamar-song-not-like-us-for-false-allegation-of-being-criminal-paedophile-3829283">起诉环球音乐集团（Universal Music G